    A[Do you have a problem in your life?]
    B[Then don't worry]
    C[Can you do something about it?]
    A--no--&gt;B;
    A--yes--&gt;C;
    C--no--&gt;B;
    C--yes--&gt;B;
```
</code></pre></div></div>

